<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id12896878-f87d-11ef-b94d-97e317d2120c" identifier="/us/usc/t4/s41"><num value="41">§ 41.</num><heading> Seal of the United States</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The seal heretofore used by the United States in Congress assembled is declared to be the seal of the United States.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id12896879-f87d-11ef-b94d-97e317d2120c">(<ref href="/us/act/1947-07-30/ch389">July 30, 1947, ch. 389</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/61/643">61 Stat. 643</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
